page.title: 17Where our parents lived.
page.content: Most people's parents in my class have not lived in Reepham all their life. Many of them have lived in Reepham between 11 to 20 years, which could mean that they had just had their child and wanted a bigger house. Eighteen people have moved here between 1 to 10 years.Twelve people have moved to Reepham in the last year and more are still coming.Only one parent has lived in Reepham between 20 to 30 years.Only three parents have lived in Reepham all thier life. Nine people's parents came from Norwich and nine from London and four from Essex.So most people's parents came from East Anglia or nearby . Five of the parents came from Sussex,Stockport ,Lincon and Hertfordshire. Three people's parents come from Scotland ,Jersey and Australia.
